---
source: crates/tk/tests/scenarios.rs
expression: "p.run(&format!(\"{command} --help\"))"
---
Update the title, body, priority, or parent of a Ticket or Epic

Usage: tk update [OPTIONS] <ID>

Arguments:
  <ID>  Display ID or Alias of the Ticket or Epic to update

Options:
  -m, --message <MESSAGE>    Message paragraph; repeatable. Conflicts with -F
  -F, --file <PATH>          Read the message from a file, or '-' for stdin
  -p, --priority <PRIORITY>  Set Priority (P0..P4). Tickets only
  -P, --parent <EPIC>        Set the containing Epic by Display ID or Alias. Tickets only
      --no-parent            Remove the Ticket from its current Epic. Tickets only
  -h, --help                 Print help
